.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, papaya, garlic, spinach
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, writing, hiking, puzzles
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, goat, fish, bird
1. the person eating papaya is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is the person eating papaya##1
4. the person eating garlic is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far right##1
6. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
7. the person eating spinach is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | garlic   | spinach      | papaya       | strawberry |
| Hobby   | chess | puzzles | hiking     | writing |
| Pet     | bird     | goat  | goldfish | fish |

