.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, iced-tea, almond-milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, scientific, superhero, romance
4 different pets are kept: pony, hedgehog, bird, cat
1. the owner of the bird is the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person watching romance movies and the owner of the pony##2
3. the person watching romance movies is the person drinking milk##1
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
5. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
6. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the person watching zombie movies is the person drinking fanta##1
8. the owner of the bird is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | almond-milk          | milk | fanta        |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero     | scientific | romance   | zombie     |
| Pet           | pony | hedgehog         | cat         | bird |

