.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, video-games, writing, hiking
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, dressmaker, designer, doctor
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, funk, salsa, folk
1. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
2. the designer is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the doctor is the person who's hobby is writing##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
5. the fan of funk is between the fisherman and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
6. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the designer##3
7. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is writing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | video-games | board-games      | writing       | hiking    |
| Job           | dressmaker  | designer  | doctor | fisherman |
| Music-Genre   | folk      | salsa | funk         | metal    |

