.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, almond-milk, hot-chocolate, sprite
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, photographer, videographer, designer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, volleyball, badminton, basketball
1. the engineer is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the engineer##3
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the engineer##3
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the engineer##1
7. the engineer is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
8. the photographer is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
9. the designer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | almond-milk         | juice  | hot-chocolate     | sprite         |
| Job        | designer | photographer | engineer | videographer         |
| Sport      | volleyball         | badminton  | biathlon   | basketball |

