.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, gospel, metal, techno
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, colombian, mexican, brazilian
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, turtle, frog, goldfish
 1. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
 2. the indian is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
 4. the mexican is between the fan of gospel and the fan of pop##2
 5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
 6. the owner of the goldfish is the fan of metal##1
 7. the brazilian is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of pop is in an odd position##4
 9. the colombian is between the fan of techno and the fan of metal##2
10. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | pop  | metal    | gospel | techno    |
| Nationality   | indian | mexican | colombian  | brazilian |
| Pet           | frog   | goldfish    | chinchilla        | turtle   |

