.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, cola, lemonade
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, designer, scientist, nurse
There are 4 different nationalities: german, french, mexican, thai
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
2. the designer is on the left of the writer##1
3. the thai is on the left or right of the scientist##3
4. the designer is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the writer##1
6. the thai is on the right of the designer##1
7. the french is on the left of the designer##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the french##3
9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate                | lemonade  | mirinda | cola   |
| Job           | nurse | designer | writer   | scientist |
| Nationality   | french         | german     | thai     | mexican |

