.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, pear, pepper, lettuce
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, documentary, adventure, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, ambient, blues, soul
1. the person eating pear is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
2. the person eating pepper is on the far left##1
3. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
5. the fan of house is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the fan of soul##2
6. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4
7. the person eating watermelon is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | pepper    | pear  | lettuce  | watermelon |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | documentary | comedy | adventure |
| Music-Genre   | blues    | house     | soul    | ambient |

