.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, juice, tea
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, nigerian, italian, german
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, goldfish, dog, cat
1. the owner of the goldfish is between the person drinking juice and the mexican##2
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
3. the italian is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the nigerian##1
5. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
7. the mexican is on the left or right of the german##3
8. the italian is the person drinking iced-tea##1
9. the german is between the owner of the dog and the owner of the guinea-pig##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | juice      | water  | tea    |
| Nationality   | italian   | nigerian | german | mexican |
| Pet           | cat      | dog       | goldfish   | guinea-pig      |

