.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, traveling, card-games, video-games
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, german, dutch, polish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, cricket, climbing, baseball
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's sport is parkour##2
3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
6. the polish is between the person who's sport is parkour and the mexican##2
7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
8. the german is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is parkour is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | fishing    | card-games | traveling  | video-games  |
| Nationality   | dutch | german       | polish | mexican |
| Sport         | climbing   | parkour      | baseball | cricket       |

