The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, time-travel, horror, scientific
4 different pets are kept: horse, chinchilla, fish, rabbit
1. the owner of the chinchilla is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the chinchilla is the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the person drinking sprite is the person watching scientific movies##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
6. the person watching thriller movies is the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
8. the owner of the rabbit is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage      | sprite      | coffee | milk     | fanta    |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | thriller      | time-travel | horror |
| Pet           | fish   | chinchilla  | horse     | rabbit |

