.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, juice, iced-tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, skateboarding, soccer, biathlon
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, skateboard, train, boat
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
2. the person who's sport is rugby is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person driving the skateboard and the person who's sport is soccer##2
6. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
8. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | juice    | hot-chocolate     | 7up    | iced-tea        |
| Sport       | soccer   | rugby | skateboarding | biathlon |
| Transport   | boat | train      | skateboard    | quad-bike   |

