4. the person who's hobby is fishing is the nurse##1
5. the french is on the right of the russian##1
6. the firefighter is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the fisherman##1
8. the polish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
