.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, peas, pumpkin, pear
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, writing, chess, puzzles
4 different pets are kept: snake, lizard, hamster, cat
1. the person eating pineapple is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
4. the person eating pumpkin is on the far left##1
5. the person eating peas is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is video-games##2
6. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
7. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
8. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person eating peas##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | pumpkin    | peas    | pineapple  | pear |
| Hobby   | puzzles | writing | video-games | chess      |
| Pet     | lizard   | snake        | cat   | hamster       |

 